    "body": "I can't point you in the right direction If I don't know how or what you're using to sign and transmit transactions. If you're running an ethereum node, then your transaction is probably propagated via the P2P network; if you're using a web API or a light wallet, then your transaction is sent via JSON RPC. \r\n\r\nYou're probably better off asking the discord server (see [here](https://discord.com/invite/nthXNEv)) or stackoverflow for help - github issues isn't the best place for these types of questions. ",
